"ebd603cd6ea0e3dde84e3dc0e53621ab0aa7bdb2","tid":1875043,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:53:15.000Z","msg":"區議會係最近一次民選結果<br />\n可唔可以內部選幾人出黎做局時代表開始搞<br />\n我地市民可以做既support就係比晒有多既口罩佢地分配<br />\n呢個時勢邊個解決到口罩問題就有影響力"},{"pid":"77740bada4a7b3f428c7efb05fa982bda6a8a099","tid":1875043,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:54:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d8d3ca419cf816a8a2082e32c2069817d91438a","tid":1875043,"uid":100155,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:55:22.000Z","msg":"Q: 面對現實連popo鎮壓都未有辦法對付，唔好講赤納米粹正規軍。我想啲實際可行方法好過啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nA: 本土政要出黎等民間支持再宣佈成立政府，<br />\n中共想即刻支爆咪鎮壓民選政權囉<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得要有軍隊係step1，咁咩都唔洗做喇，去搶口罩吧啦<br />\n<br />\n失敗撚充斥連登，方案係一齊討論出黎<br />\n你想個天跌落嚟俾我哋？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ: 人哋委內瑞拉有美國支持都未成功奪到權<br />\nA: 起碼人地行左十步啦<br />\n香港仲訓緊諗緊點一步登天<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ: 國際唔理<br />\nA: 承唔承認係美國話事，參考委內瑞拉，美國支持民選內閣，反對獨裁及中共支持嘅馬杜羅。<br />\n你唔試又點知？"},{"pid":"172f8ecabcc28da29f443a8cc19f8b85df3f0ebd","tid":1875043,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2f7e060dcc1d838570ca7593ec70b2fe0073acd","tid":1875043,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gk8EoQJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgk8EoQJ.png&h=60abdd68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特區政府（又稱港共傀儡政權）由組成到管治都毫無正當性。<br />\n<br />\n港人應學委內瑞拉，自組港人政府，再予美國及西方承認<br />\n<br />\n認同請推po"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VJVCVeK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVJVCVeK.png&h=3adda73d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BQPwfeL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBQPwfeL.p